Geospatial, racial, and educational variation in firearm mortality in the USA, 
Mexico, Brazil, and Colombia, 1990-2015: a comparative analysis of vital 
statistics data.

Dare AJ(1), Irving H(1), Guerrero-López CM(2), Watson LK(1), Kolpak P(1), 
Reynales Shigematsu LM(2), Sanches M(3), Gomez D(4), Gelband H(5), Jha P(6).

